r performance. The default value is 128.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionBuffer"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionClipsCoordinates":{"abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing a Boolean value; specifies whether the shape of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" should be clipped at the edge of each tile. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"default value is ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionClipsCoordinates","title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClipsCoordinates","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClipsCoordinates","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionclipscoordinates","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionSimplificationTolerance":{"title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionSimplificationTolerance","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionSimplificationTolerance","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionsimplificationtolerance","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSNumber","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" object containing a double; specifies the Douglas-Peucker","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"simplification tolerance. A greater value produces simpler geometries and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"improves performance. The default value is 0.375.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionSimplificationTolerance","kind":"identifier"}]}}}